<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@100..900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: Noto Sans KR, system-ui, Avenir, Helvetica, Arial,
          sans-serif;
      }
      .container {
        width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .logo {
        width: 120px;
        height: 28px;
        object-fit: contain;
        margin-top: 50px;
      }
      .title {
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 26px;
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: -0.78px;
      }
      .payment-details {
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: -0.54px;
      }
      .payment-info {
        border-top: 1px solid #161a3f;
        margin-top: 20px;
        width: 100%;
        border-spacing: 0;
      }

      .payment-info tbody tr td {
        padding: 15px;
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: -0.42px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaf4;
      }
      .payment-info tbody tr td:first-child {
        color: #5c5f79;
        background: #fafafd;
      }
      ul {
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding-left: 15px;
      }
      ul li {
        color: #8d8fa2;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 24px;
        letter-spacing: -0.39px;
      }

      .button {
        padding: 14px 48px;
        border: 1px solid #2d40ff;
        background-color: #2d40ff;
        color: #fff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: -0.28px;
      }
      .table-button {
        margin-top: 30px;
        width: 100%;
      }
      .table-button tr td {
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 50px;
      }
      .footer .phone-icon {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        object-fit: contain;
      }
      .footer .phone {
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 500;
        line-height: 22px; /* 91.667% */
        letter-spacing: -0.96px;
        display: inline-block;
      }
      .footer .work-hour {
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;
        line-height: 22px;
        vertical-align: top;
        letter-spacing: -0.56px;
      }
      .links span {
        display: inline-block;
        color: #2d40ff;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 26px;
        letter-spacing: -0.52px;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
      .info span {
        color: #5b5d75;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 26px;
        letter-spacing: -0.52px;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
      .footer-logo {
        margin-top: 11px;
      }
      .footer-logo span {
        color: #5b5d75;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 26px;
        letter-spacing: -0.52px;
        vertical-align: top;
      }
      .footer-logo img {
        width: 23px;
        height: 23px;
        object-fit: contain;
      }
      .booking-code {
        text-align: center;
      }

      .booking-code p:first-child {
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 14px;
        letter-spacing: -0.42px;
      }
      .booking-code p:last-child {
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.4px;
      }
      .booking-info p:first-child {
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: -0.45px;
      }
      .booking-info span {
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 14px;
        letter-spacing: -0.28px;
        font-weight: 400;
      }
      .booking-info p:last-child {
        color: #ff176b;
        font-size: 20px;
        letter-spacing: -0.4px;
      }

      .hotel-info thead tr th {
        padding: 15px 30px;
        text-align: left;
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: -0.42px;
        background: #fafafd;
      }
      .hotel-info tbody tr td {
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: -0.42px;
        background-color: #fff !important;
        padding: 15px 30px;
      }
      .booked-amount {
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: -0.54px;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
      h4 {
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: -0.42px;
        margin: 16px 0 50px;
      }
      h4 a {
        color: #06f;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <img
        class="logo"
        src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/app-snab.appspot.com/o/Frame.jpg?alt=media&token=ed6e3e96-6c5d-4112-b09f-b5ad3fcd470b"
      />
      <h1 class="title">
        귀하의 계정에서 비정상적인 로그인 시도가 감지되었습니다.
      </h1>
      <h4>
        <a href="mailto: <%=email%>"><%=email%></a> 계정이 새로운 IP 주소에서
        접속된 것으로 확인되었습니다.
      </h4>

      <p class="booked-amount">결제내역</p>
      <table class="payment-info hotel-info">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>접속일시</th>
            <th>IP 주소</th>
            <th>OS</th>
            <th>브라우저</th>
            <th>디바이스</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td><%=date%></td>
            <td><%=ipAddress%></td>
            <td><%=os%></td>
            <td><%=browser%></td>
            <td><%=deviceType%></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <ul>
        <li>
          이 활동을 인식하지 못하시나요? 비밀번호를 재설정하고 즉시
          <a href="mailto:wafl@wafflestay.kr">wafl@wafflestay.kr</a>으로
          연락주세요.
        </li>
        <li>이 메시지는 자동으로 발송되는 메시지입니다. 회신하지 마세요.</li>
      </ul>
      <table class="table-button">
        <tr>
          <td>
            <a href="<%=resetPasswordUrl%>" target="_blank">
              <button class="button">비밀번호 변경</button>
            </a>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>